@startuml
title Sequence Diagram Pembaruan Profil Alumni
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Alumni" as Alumni
boundary "Halaman Update Profil" as View
control "UpdateProfile (Livewire)" as Update
control "Auth" as Auth
entity "AlumniProfile" as Profile
collections "Storage Publik" as Storage
database "Database" as DB

Alumni -> View : Buka Update Profil
View -> Update : mount()
Update -> Auth : user()
Auth --> Update : User aktif
Update -> Profile : user.alumniProfile
Profile -> DB : SELECT profil
DB --> Update : Data profil
Update --> View : Isi formulir profil

opt Mengelola prestasi
  Alumni -> View : Tambah/hapus prestasi
  View -> Update : addAchievement()/removeAchievement()
  Update --> View : Perbarui daftar prestasi
end

Alumni -> View : Ubah data dan simpan
View -> Update : save()
Update -> Update : Validasi data dan foto
opt Foto baru tersedia
  Update -> Storage : storePublicly(alumni-photos)
  Storage --> Update : Path foto
end
Update -> Profile : update(data, achievements, photo_url)
Profile -> DB : UPDATE alumni_profiles
DB --> Update : Berhasil
Update --> View : Toast profil berhasil diperbarui
View --> Alumni : Tampilkan profil terbaru
@enduml
